    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a perfect blend of performance and everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like shine, with only the most minor, superficial stone chips on the lower valance consistent with careful road use. Step inside to a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show minimal wear. All interior electronics, including the navigation system and heated seats, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and dry, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule\u2014most recently receiving a full fluid service and new brake pads. It drives straight and true, with a suspension that remains firm yet comfortable. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
